{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Range","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Range","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\"><code>Range()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/collapsed\"><code>collapsed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/commonAncestorContainer\"><code>commonAncestorContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/endContainer\"><code>endContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/endOffset\"><code>endOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/startContainer\"><code>startContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset\"><code>startOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneContents\"><code>cloneContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneRange\"><code>cloneRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/collapse\"><code>collapse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareBoundaryPoints\"><code>compareBoundaryPoints()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareNode\"><code>compareNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/comparePoint\"><code>comparePoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/createContextualFragment\"><code>createContextualFragment()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/deleteContents\"><code>deleteContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/detach\"><code>detach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/extractContents\"><code>extractContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>getBoundingClientRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>insertNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>intersectsNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>selectNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>selectNodeContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>setEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>setStart()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>setStartBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>surroundContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>Range</code></strong> interface represents a fragment of a document that can contain nodes and parts of text nodes.</p>\n\n<p>A range can be created using the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/createRange\"><code>createRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;method of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>&nbsp;object. Range objects can also be retrieved by using the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Selection/getRangeAt\"><code>getRangeAt()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;method of the&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;object or the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/caretRangeFromPoint\"><code>caretRangeAtPoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> method of the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> object.</p>\n\n<p>There also is the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\" title=\"Range()\"><code>Range()</code></a> constructor available.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>There are no inherited properties.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"range.collapsed_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/collapsed\"><code>Range.collapsed</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indicating whether the range's start and end points are at the same position.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.commonancestorcontainer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/commonAncestorContainer\"><code>Range.commonAncestorContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the deepest&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp;that contains the <code>startContainer</code> and <code>endContainer</code> nodes.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.endcontainer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/endContainer\"><code>Range.endContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp;within which the <code>Range</code> ends.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.endoffset_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/endOffset\"><code>Range.endOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a number representing where in the <code>endContainer</code> the <code>Range</code> ends.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.startcontainer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/startContainer\"><code>Range.startContainer</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp;within which the <code>Range</code> starts.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.startoffset_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/startOffset\"><code>Range.startOffset</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a number representing where in the <code>startContainer</code> the <code>Range</code> starts.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"range\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range/Range\" title=\"Range()\"><code>Range()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <code>Range</code> object with the global <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a> as its start and end.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>There are no inherited methods.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"range.setstart_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStart\"><code>Range.setStart()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the start position of a <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setend_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEnd\"><code>Range.setEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the end position of a <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setstartbefore_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartBefore\"><code>Range.setStartBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the start position of a <code>Range</code> relative to another&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setstartafter_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setStartAfter\"><code>Range.setStartAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the start position of a <code>Range</code> relative to another&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setendbefore_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndBefore\"><code>Range.setEndBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the end position of a <code>Range</code> relative to another&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.setendafter_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/setEndAfter\"><code>Range.setEndAfter()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the end position of a <code>Range</code> relative to another&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.selectnode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNode\"><code>Range.selectNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the <code>Range</code> to contain the&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp;and its contents.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.selectnodecontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/selectNodeContents\"><code>Range.selectNodeContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Sets the <code>Range</code> to contain the contents of a&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.collapse_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/collapse\"><code>Range.collapse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Collapses the <code>Range</code> to one of its boundary points.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.clonecontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneContents\"><code>Range.cloneContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a>&nbsp;copying the nodes of a <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.deletecontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/deleteContents\"><code>Range.deleteContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Removes the contents of a <code>Range</code> from the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.extractcontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/extractContents\"><code>Range.extractContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Moves contents of a <code>Range</code> from the document tree into a&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.insertnode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/insertNode\"><code>Range.insertNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Insert a&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>&nbsp;at the start of a <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.surroundcontents_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/surroundContents\"><code>Range.surroundContents()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Moves content of a <code>Range</code> into a new&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.compareboundarypoints_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareBoundaryPoints\"><code>Range.compareBoundaryPoints()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Compares the boundary points of the <code>Range</code> with another <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.clonerange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/cloneRange\"><code>Range.cloneRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <code>Range</code> object with boundary points identical to the cloned <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.detach_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/detach\"><code>Range.detach()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Releases the <code>Range</code> from use to improve performance.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.tostring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/toString\"><code>Range.toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns the text of the <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.comparenode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/compareNode\"><code>Range.compareNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon obsolete\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>Dies ist eine veraltete API und es wird nicht mehr garantiert, dass sie funktioniert.</title>\n    <path d=\"M38.75 78.13V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0036.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0033.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0051.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0048.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0066.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0063.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zM36.88 20h26.25l-2.82-6.85a2.35 2.35 0 00-1-.65H40.74a2 2 0 00-1 .65zm54.37 1.88v3.75a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.87 1.87h-5.63v55.55c0 6.44-4.22 12-9.37 12H25.63c-5.16 0-9.38-5.27-9.38-11.72V27.5h-5.62a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.88-1.83v-3.8A1.85 1.85 0 0110.63 20h18.1l4.1-9.78A9.12 9.12 0 0140.63 5h18.75a9.1 9.1 0 017.79 5.22l4.1 9.78h18.11a1.85 1.85 0 011.87 1.87z\"></path>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a constant representing whether the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a> is before, after, inside, or surrounding the range.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.comparepoint_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/comparePoint\"><code>Range.comparePoint()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns -1, 0, or 1 indicating whether the point occurs before, inside, or after the <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.createcontextualfragment_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/createContextualFragment\"><code>Range.createContextualFragment()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a>&nbsp;created from a given string of code.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.getboundingclientrect_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getBoundingClientRect\"><code>Range.getBoundingClientRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> object which bounds the entire contents of the <code>Range</code>; this would be the union of all the rectangles returned by <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>range.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.getclientrects_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/getClientRects\"><code>Range.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a list of <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> objects that aggregates the results of <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/getClientRects\"><code>Element.getClientRects()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> for all the elements in the <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.intersectsnode_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/intersectsNode\"><code>Range.intersectsNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <code>boolean</code> indicating whether the given node intersects the <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"range.ispointinrange_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Range/isPointInRange\"><code>Range.isPointInRange()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <code>boolean</code> indicating whether the given point is in the <code>Range</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-range\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Range' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Do not use <code>RangeException</code> anymore, use <code>DOMException</code> instead.<br>\n    Made the second parameter of <code>collapse()</code> optional.<br>\n    Added the methods <code>isPointInRange()</code>, <code>comparePoint()</code>, and <code>intersectsNode()</code>.<br>\n    Added the constructor <code>Range()</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/DOM-Parsing/#extensions-to-the-range-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Parsing and Serialization<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Extensions to Range' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Added the method <code>createContextualFragment()</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#extensions-to-the-range-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Extensions to Range' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Added the methods <code>getClientRects()</code> and <code>getBoundingClientRect()</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Traversal-Range/ranges.html#Level-2-Range-Interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Traversal and Range Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Range' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher) [1]</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>Range()</code> constructor <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/24\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2013-09-17.\">24.0</a> (24.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>compareNode()</code> <svg class=\"icon obsolete\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"img\">\n    <title>Dies ist eine veraltete API und es wird nicht mehr garantiert, dass sie funktioniert.</title>\n    <path d=\"M38.75 78.13V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0036.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0033.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0051.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0048.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zm15 0V36.88A1.85 1.85 0 0066.88 35h-3.75a1.85 1.85 0 00-1.88 1.88v41.25A1.85 1.85 0 0063.13 80h3.75a1.85 1.85 0 001.87-1.87zM36.88 20h26.25l-2.82-6.85a2.35 2.35 0 00-1-.65H40.74a2 2 0 00-1 .65zm54.37 1.88v3.75a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.87 1.87h-5.63v55.55c0 6.44-4.22 12-9.37 12H25.63c-5.16 0-9.38-5.27-9.38-11.72V27.5h-5.62a1.85 1.85 0 01-1.88-1.83v-3.8A1.85 1.85 0 0110.63 20h18.1l4.1-9.78A9.12 9.12 0 0140.63 5h18.75a9.1 9.1 0 017.79 5.22l4.1 9.78h18.11a1.85 1.85 0 011.87 1.87z\"></path>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 oder früher)<br>\n    Removed in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>isPointInRange()</code>, and <code>comparePoint()</code><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>intersectsNode()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/17\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2012-11-20.\">17.0</a> (17.0) [2]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>getClientRects()</code> and <code>getBoundingClientRect()</code><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>9</td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td>5</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>createContextualFragment()</code><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td>15.0</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.0) [1]</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Starting with Gecko 13.0 (Firefox 13.0 / Thunderbird 13.0 / SeaMonkey 2.10) the <code>Range</code> object throws a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> as defined in DOM 4, instead of a <code>RangeException</code> defined in prior specifications.</p>\n\n<p>[2] Gecko supported it up to Gecko 1.9, then removed it until Gecko 17 where it was reimplemented, matching the spec.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\" title=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/DOM_Reference\">The DOM interfaces index</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The Range interface represents a fragment of a document that can contain nodes and parts of text nodes.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Range","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"range","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"range","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Range","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"range","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"range","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Range","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Range","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title